alert tcp any any -> any 80
drop udp any any -> any 53
alert tcp -> any 80
pass icmp any any <> any any
alert tcp 10.1.2.3 any -> any 443
drop udp $HOME_NET 5353 -> any any
alert icmp any any -> 192.168.0.0/16 any
pass tcp any 22 -> any 2222
drop icmp 172.16.1.1 any <> $EXTERNAL_NET any
alert udp any any -> any 123
